law.history: Repealed 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 69 effective December 1, 1972. -- Amended 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 23, sec. 1, effective June 18, 1970. -- Amended 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 120, sec. 5, effective June 14, 1962. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 242, sec. 6, effective March 23, 1946.
